cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CG 

This paper deals with the problem of learning implicit surfaces from 2D images, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper also proposes a novel ray-based field probing technique and a geometric regularizer, which are both related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper addresses the issue of precise geometric properties and control, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG).
